#Program will calculate your return day
#-----------------------------#
start_day = int(input("Enter starting day (0-6): "))
Enter starting day (0-6): 3
stay_length = int(input("Enter length of stay: "))
Enter length of stay: 10
return_day = (start_day + stay_length) % 7
print("You will return on day", return_day)
You will return on day 6
